parameters:
????: "Congratulations. As promised, you've collected the
gold coins 'Spintriae'. This is a proof of trust. You have
earned my trust."

????: "That's right. A paradise only for the chosen ones
like you to enter. That is the 'Kingdom'."

????: "You should spread your wings to your heart's content.
Be freed from the shackles of reality..."

????: "You'll understand once you proceed. The splendor of
this place, that is."

\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "No, I mean... the ticket...! I joined the game
because I wanted a ticket. I wanted to go to an idol concert
with Himawari-chan..."
\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "Could it be that I've been... deceived?"

????: "I haven't deceived you. I said I would prepare what
you desire..."

\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "But... my wish was to go to the concert with
Himawari-chan..."

????: "What you desire is here. You just didn't know it
until you came here."
